name: Ego Death
description:
And just like that the ceiling opened up and I was out of my body, flung through space and time, existing not as myself, but an infantile being simply observing, untethered by time, attempting to take in the vast information overload of folding realities playing out before me.

A halloween gift to my early NFT supporters!
This imagery was created by training a portrait machine learning algorithm on a massive photo collection of neon skulls and blacklight facepaint.
